shape: sequence_diagram

Client: API Client
Gateway: Gateway
Authorization: Credential & Authorization Service
Entitlement: Entitlement & Usage Service
Ledger: Usage Ledger
Upstream: Upstream API

Client -> Gateway: Send request with machine credential
Gateway -> Authorization: Validate credential, route, scopes, and policy
Authorization -> Gateway: Return authorized project context
Gateway -> Entitlement: Reserve required usage unit
Entitlement -> Ledger: Create reservation with request identity
Ledger -> Entitlement: Reservation accepted or rejected
Entitlement -> Gateway: Return reservation result
Gateway -> Upstream: Forward request when reserved
Upstream -> Gateway: Return upstream outcome
Gateway -> Entitlement: Confirm or release reservation
Entitlement -> Ledger: Finalize usage transaction
Gateway -> Client: Return response
